Usage: get_ccopt_clock_tree_slew [-help] <instTerm|term>
                                 [-edge {rise fall both}] [ -delay_corner <delay_corner> ] [ -delay_type <type> ]

-help                            # Prints out the command usage
<instTerm|term>                  # pin to query slew for
                                 # ((instTerm|term), required)
-delay_corner <delay_corner>     # the delay corner to query
                                 # ((delay_corner), optional)
-delay_type {early late}         # for this delay type (enum, optional)
-edge {rise fall both}           # for this edge (enum, optional)